  "prompt": "Which is a good solar panel installation provider in San Dimas, California CA?",
  "response": "If you're looking for reputable solar panel installation providers in San Dimas, California, you have several options. Some highly-rated providers in the area include:\n\n1. **SunPower by Stellar Solar**: Known for high efficiency panels and strong customer service.\n2. **Momentum Solar**: Offers personalized solar energy solutions and handling of all permits and paperwork.\n3. **Infinity Solar**: Locally known with strong reviews for residential solar installations.\n4. **SolarMAX Technology**: Provides comprehensive solar solutions and financing options.\n5. **Vivint Solar**: Nationally recognized brand with customized solar solutions and flexible financing.\n\nIt's always a good idea to get quotes from multiple providers, check customer reviews, and evaluate their credentials such as licensing and certifications before making a decision. Also, consider looking at the Better Business Bureau ratings, and checking if they have any complaints or issues that have been reported.",
